      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "OREGON CALDWELL (1) missed the frame last time when fourth (23.47) at this track but prior to that had four placings in a row. Solid record here winning seven races. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Can make amends. VOSS ALI (5) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 2 lengths into second (23.29) at this track in a Other over 400m. Expected to be in the finish again. STARLIGHT JEWEL (8) finds it hard to break through. Finished third (23.32) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Form at the trip sound including six wins. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Expected to be in the finish again. RUSTY WHEELS (4) was in the money two back in a Other at this track then jumped from a squeeze draw last time and was not far away when third (23.43) over 400m at this track. Safe beginner who will go forward from trap four.",
